-- Obama Defense Strategy Emphasizes Asia, Internet
-- B y
-- 2012-01-05T19:32:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/obama-defense-strategy-emphasizes-asia-internet.html
U.S. President  Barack Obama , Defense 
Secretary  Leon Panetta  and Army General Martin Dempsey, chairman
of the Joint Chiefs of Staff, speak about the Defense 
Department's global strategy and budget at the Pentagon.  Obama presented a revamped military strategy for an era of 
budget cuts that pledges to emphasize  Asia  and space and cyber 
capabilities while preserving missions such as defeating 
al-Qaeda. (Source: Bloomberg)  00:00 Obama: "moment of transition" in strategy
11:18 Panetta discusses defense tactics, budget.
32:57 Dempsey: collaboration to develop strategy
39:03 Panetta, Dempsey respond to questions.  Running time 52:25
 